nodes.text: This Inn was located in Cuipernam, capital city of the planet Ansion. In 22 BBY it was the site of a skirmish between Jedi Master Luminara Unduli and her Padawan Barriss Offee and mercenaries hired by Ogomoor, majordomo to Soergg the Hutt. It was later destroyed in a second skirmish that took place in Cuipernam.
